comment: Go to on a high class night. Impress the friends with the price, but it isn’t as good as some of the knob creeks out there.

Light bite on pallet at the end 
Smooth start 
Vanilla and creams.

Low viscosity
Nose - sweet, salty, 
Palate - herbal and floral, spicy/heat. maybe even slight oily. Low in vanilla and tobacco.
